claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table of solicited local and systemic adverse reactions (e.g., pain, redness, fatigue, headache, muscle pain, fever) following vaccination with Flublok and comparators, accompanied by footnotes detailing data collection, study identifiers, and definitions of severity.
